<div class="layout">
  
  <div class="sidebar">
    
    <div class="control-panel">
      <h3>Layout Settings</h3>
      
      <div class="settings-section">
        <h4>Paper Settings</h4>
        <p>This section defines the physical paper size you'll be printing on - the actual sheet that goes in your printer.</p>
        <div class="setting-group" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
          <label for="paper-size" style="flex: 0 0 90px;">Paper Size:</label>
          <select id="paper-size" style="flex: 1; height: 32px; padding: 6px; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 3px;">
            <option value="letter">Letter (8.5" × 11")</option>
            <option value="legal">Legal (8.5" × 14")</option>
            <option value="a4">A4 (210mm × 297mm)</option>
            <option value="custom">Custom</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        
        <div id="custom-paper-size" class="setting-group hidden">
          <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px;">
            <div style="flex: 1; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
              <label for="paper-width" style="flex: 0 0 80px;">Width (in):</label>
              <input type="number" id="paper-width" value="8.5" step="0.1" min="3" max="48" style="flex: 1; max-width: 80px; height: 32px; padding: 6px; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box;">
            </div>
            <div style="flex: 1; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
              <label for="paper-height" style="flex: 0 0 80px;">Height (in):</label>
              <input type="number" id="paper-height" value="11" step="0.1" min="3" max="48" style="flex: 1; max-width: 80px; height: 32px; padding: 6px; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box;">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="setting-group" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
          <label for="paper-orientation" style="flex: 0 0 90px;">Orientation:</label>
          <select id="paper-orientation" style="flex: 1; height: 32px; padding: 6px; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 3px;">
            <option value="portrait">Portrait</option>
            <option value="landscape">Landscape</option>
          </select>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="settings-section">
        <h4>Cell Configuration</h4>
        <p>Configure the size and layout of individual cells (labels) that will be printed on your paper.</p>
        <div class="setting-group" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
          <label for="panel-preset" style="flex: 0 0 110px;">Preset Layouts:</label>
          <select id="panel-preset" style="flex: 1; height: 32px; padding: 6px; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 3px;">
            <option value="custom">Custom Configuration</option>
            <option value="address">Address Labels (30 per sheet, 1" × 2.625")</option>
            <option value="shipping">Shipping Labels (6 per sheet, 4" × 3.33")</option>
            <option value="name-badge">Name Badges (10 per sheet, 2" × 4")</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        
        <div id="custom-panel-config">
          <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px;">
